==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Plashing
<hw>Plash"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The cutting or
bending and intertwining the branches of small trees, as in
hedges.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The dashing or sprinkling of coloring matter on the
walls of buildings, to imitate granite, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plashoot</ent>⟦br⟧
